Notes: Erin Evans hits a turnaround jumper in the lane with 4.3 seconds to go to give
Oakland City the win...UMR led by as many as 10 points in the second half...
UMR's Felicia Johns missed a potential game-winning shot at the buzzer.
Game.Officials: Jim Dunlap,  Joe Calezzaro,  Fred Steele
